So, basically, the point is
that, when a firm does R&D,

00:29:14.410 --> 00:29:17.830
they do it until the
benefits to the firm

00:29:17.830 --> 00:29:19.340
equal the costs to the firm.

00:29:19.340 --> 00:29:24.210
So they do an optimum-- they do
