00:31:02.490 --> 00:31:03.574
Yeah?

00:31:03.574 --> 00:31:05.520
STUDENT: Why would the
social marginal cost

00:31:05.520 --> 00:31:08.545
go down when the social
marginal benefit goes up?

00:31:08.545 --> 00:31:10.420
JONATHAN GRUBER: Because
